{"tid":1777154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛山病死豬肉被蓋「檢驗合格」","createTime":"2019-12-10T04:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T04:56:34.000Z","uid":121580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a96aabf7ed410de8e22eed4a9e5099802149b0","tid":1777154,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2515863/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2515863%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9a496f13\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2515863/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每日數千斤發黑豬肉流入市場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n據廣東廣播電視台《今日一線》長達一個月的調查，記者發現廣東佛山一家正規的豬肉屠宰場，竟私下屠宰病死豬。廣東廣播電視台記者見到一名男子將一隻重達三、四百斤的死豬，從活豬交易區直接拖到宰殺區。一開始，工作人員拒絕分割這條死豬，但男子隨後找了另外幾名身穿屠宰場制服的人員聊一聊，然後死豬就被工作人員拉上屠宰區。<br />\n<br />\n詳細㩒入link睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n願藍絲門共享中華榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36f9bbe0539d990bc234a0f90563f826261cd0c","tid":1777154,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"內文講條片既link呢"},{"pid":"954715d77cd1ab74df1a876960739ccc772dafa3","tid":1777154,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:46:20.000Z","msg":"請藍屍們優先享用！！！！！"},{"pid":"a53ac264263baafb4af77df0ae9fca565178c888","tid":1777154,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"祖國送大禮!"},{"pid":"6fa25ec43b6efdfd6e86c3dc7a751579e450c165","tid":1777154,"uid":65091,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"佛山病死豬冇病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fb2f10ee051ed153f754a8d559e9845d30fe4f","tid":1777154,"uid":210669,